cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with object detection, which is a core problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves online learning, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method also involves linear discriminant analysis, which is a technique used in neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on handwritten digit and face datasets, which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
